title: Rookery Bay Adventure Race
text:
8:00 a.m. Saturday, Nov. 21, 2015 Categories 
Events, Sports The Adventure Race includes a 3K Kayak Route along Henderson Creek and a 4K Trail Run at the Rookery Bay Environmental Learning Center. New this year is a 5K Trail Run-only category. All participants will receive a t-shirt (sizes guaranteed if registered before Oct. 31), post-race refreshments, Rookery Bay Reserve water bottle, free admission to the Environmental Learning Center and entry for door prizes. Awards will be presented to the top finishers in each category: men, women, relays, tandem-teams and surf-skis. The race is presented by Up A Creek Kayak Tours and benefits Friends of Rookery Bay, with support from Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission.
